cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper deals with reinforcement learning in robotics tasks, which involves both machine learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves the use of demonstrations, which falls under the category of imitation learning, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The tasks involve visual perception, which falls under the category of computer vision, making cs.CV (Computer Vision) a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with control and optimization, which falls under the category of control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category as well.
